HOUSE JOINT RESOLUTION 1026
By Darby
A RESOLUTION to congratulate Ali Ridgeway on being named
the 2026 Hostess Princess of the 73rd Annual
World's Biggest Fish Fry and Jayla Boutwell,
Kylee French, Madeline Gottshall, and Madison
Melton on being named the 2026 Hostess
Princess Court.
WHEREAS, the members of this General Assembly are pleased to specially recognize
those outstanding young women of this State whose poise, admirable personality traits, and
beauty, both inner and outer, make them role models among their peers; and
WHEREAS, five such outstanding young women from Henry County include Ali
Ridgeway, who was named 2026 Hostess Princess, and Jayla Boutwell, Kylee French,
Madeline Gottshall, and Madison Melton, who were selected as members of the 2026 Hostess
Princess Court in honor of the festivities of the 73rd Annual World's Biggest Fish Fry sponsored
by the Paris-Henry County Jaycees in Paris, Tennessee; and
WHEREAS, for more than seven decades, the World's Biggest Fish Fry has brought
acclaim and recognition to Paris; this renowned festival features a full week of activities for all
ages and is conducted for members of the community and visitors alike to enjoy; and
WHEREAS, the 2026 Hostess Princess is Ali Ridgeway, a senior at Henry County High
School and the daughter of Brad and Angie Ridgeway; and
WHEREAS, the 2026 Hostess Princess Court is composed of first maid Jayla Boutwell,
second maid Kylee French, third maid Madeline Gottshall, and fourth maid Madison Melton; and
WHEREAS, these young ladies' beauty, grace, drive, and determination are sources of
pride for their parents, their families, and their communities and bode well for their future
successes; and
HJR1026
013944
- 1 -

WHEREAS, it is fitting that we specially recognize and honor the Hostess Princess and
her Court, five of Tennessee's most promising young women; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE ONE HUNDRED
FOURTEENTH GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, THE SENATE
CONCURRING, that we honor and congratulate Ali Ridgeway on being named 2026 Hostess
Princess of the 73rd Annual World's Biggest Fish Fry in Paris, Tennessee; likewise, we honor
Jayla Boutwell, Kylee French, Madeline Gottshall, and Madison Melton on being named to the
2026 Hostess Princess Court and extend to these exceptional young ladies our best wishes for
every success in all their future endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy and upon proper request made to
the appropriate clerk, the language appearing immediately following the State seal appear
without House or Senate designation.
